title: Unreleased Stogies & More!
itunes:title: Unreleased Stogies & More!
description: This week on The Cigar Authority David Garofalo, Mr. Jonathan and Chuck Morrison are smoking all unreleased cigars including Jesus L. Fuego new Sangre de Toro and EP Carillo Conn. Joining us is Matt Wyrick from www.CigarThinkTank.com, and Tim Peirce from www.FitTrue.com. It's time for the finer things in life... It's time for The Cigar Authority!
